  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Emergency Appeal seeks  CHF 11.6 million to support two National Societies &#x2013; Democratic Republic of Congo Red Cross Society (DRC RC) and Rwanda Red Cross Society (RRCS) to deliver humanitarian assistance to and support early recovery for some 80,0000 people (displaced and host communities) in the Democratic Republic of Congo (70,000 people) and Rwanda (10,000 people) affected by multiple hazards and compounding humanitarian vulnerabilities caused by the eruption of Mount Nyiragongo for a period of 12 months.</narrative>
